headline: Raymond James (NYSE:RJF) Surprises With Q3 Sales
summary: Financial services firm Raymond James Financial (NYSE:RJF) reported Q3 CY2025 results exceeding the market’s revenue expectations, with sales up 7.7% year on year to $3.73 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $3.11 per share was 10% above analysts’ consensus estimates.

headline: Raymond James Financial, Inc. (RJF) Q4 Earnings and Revenues Top Estimates
summary: Raymond James Financial (RJF) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +15.19% and +3.52%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
